    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# 🎬 MPT Agent System — Gemini Colab Runner\n",
        "> **Runtime: Standard (CPU)** — no GPU needed.\n",
        ">\n",
        "> Pipeline: TrendScout → ScriptWriter (Gemini) → VideoProducer (MPT + Pexels) → SEO (Gemini) → Publisher (optional)\n",
        ">\n",
        "> Run cells **top to bottom, one at a time**. Do NOT skip Step 2."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": ["## ✅ Step 1 — Install everything"]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step1_install"},
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "\n",
        "# System packages required by MoviePy (MPT's video renderer)\n",
        "print('Installing system packages...')\n",
        "!apt-get install -y -q imagemagick ffmpeg > /dev/null 2>&1\n",
        "# Allow ImageMagick to write files (Colab policy blocks it by default)\n",
        "!sed -i 's/rights=\"none\" pattern=\"PDF\"/rights=\"read|write\" pattern=\"PDF\"/g' /etc/ImageMagick-6/policy.xml 2>/dev/null || true\n",
        "!sed -i 's/<policy domain=\"path\" rights=\"none\" pattern=\"@\*\"\/>/<policy domain=\"path\" rights=\"read|write\" pattern=\"@\*\"\//g' /etc/ImageMagick-6/policy.xml 2>/dev/null || true\n",
        "print('System packages ready.')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Clone MoneyPrinterTurbo\n",
        "if not os.path.exists('/content/MoneyPrinterTurbo'):\n",
        "    !git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/harry0703/MoneyPrinterTurbo.git /content/MoneyPrinterTurbo\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    !cd /content/MoneyPrinterTurbo && git pull --quiet\n",
        "print('MPT cloned.')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Install MPT Python dependencies\n",
        "!pip install -q -r /content/MoneyPrinterTurbo/requirements.txt 2>&1 | tail -5\n",
        "!pip install -q loguru edge-tts 'moviepy==1.0.3' imageio-ffmpeg toml 2>&1 | tail -3\n",
        "\n",
        "# Clone agent system (or pull latest)\n",
        "if not os.path.exists('/content/mpt-agent-system'):\n",
        "    !git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/Bhushan-Khachane/mpt-agent-system.git /content/mpt-agent-system\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    !cd /content/mpt-agent-system && git pull\n",
        "\n",
        "# Install agent dependencies\n",
        "!pip install -q feedparser pytrends requests google-api-python-client google-auth-httplib2 google-auth-oauthlib 2>&1 | tail -3\n",
        "\n",
        "print('\n✅ All dependencies installed.')"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 🔑 Step 2 — API Keys\n",
        "\n",
        "| Key | Where to get | Format |\n",
        "|-----|-------------|--------|\n",
        "| Gemini | https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey | Starts with `AIza` |\n",
        "| Pexels | https://www.pexels.com/api/ | Long alphanumeric string |\n",
        "| Pixabay | https://pixabay.com/api/docs/ | Optional |\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step2_config"},
      "source": [
        "import os, sys, pathlib\n",
        "\n",
        "# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n",
        "GEMINI_API_KEY  = 'AIza...'          # REQUIRED: get free at aistudio.google.com\n",
        "PEXELS_API_KEY  = 'YOUR_PEXELS_KEY'  # REQUIRED: get free at pexels.com/api\n",
        "PIXABAY_API_KEY = ''                 # optional\n",
        "# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n",
        "\n",
        "# Validate\n",
        "if not GEMINI_API_KEY.startswith('AIza') or len(GEMINI_API_KEY) < 30:\n",
        "    raise ValueError('Invalid Gemini key. Must start with AIza. Get it free: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey')\n",
        "if PEXELS_API_KEY in ('YOUR_PEXELS_KEY', '', None):\n",
        "    raise ValueError('Invalid Pexels key. Get it free: https://www.pexels.com/api/')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Set environment variables\n",
        "os.environ['GEMINI_API_KEY']   = GEMINI_API_KEY\n",
        "os.environ['GEMINI_MODEL']     = 'gemini-2.0-flash'\n",
        "os.environ['PEXELS_API_KEY']   = PEXELS_API_KEY\n",
        "os.environ['PIXABAY_API_KEY']  = PIXABAY_API_KEY\n",
        "os.environ['MPT_DIR']          = '/content/MoneyPrinterTurbo'\n",
        "os.environ['YT_CHANNEL_AI']    = 'UCxxxxxxxx'\n",
        "os.environ['YT_CHANNEL_CLEAN'] = 'UCxxxxxxxx'\n",
        "os.environ['YT_CHANNEL_MONEY'] = 'UCxxxxxxxx'\n",
        "\n",
        "# Add agent system to Python path\n",
        "AGENT_ROOT = '/content/mpt-agent-system'\n",
        "if AGENT_ROOT not in sys.path:\n",
        "    sys.path.insert(0, AGENT_ROOT)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Create required directories and seed empty JSON files\n",
        "for d in ['data', 'videos', 'logs', 'credentials']:\n",
        "    pathlib.Path(f'{AGENT_ROOT}/{d}').mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n",
        "for fp, default in [\n",
        "    (f'{AGENT_ROOT}/data/topics_queue.json', '[]'),\n",
        "    (f'{AGENT_ROOT}/data/seen_topics.json',  '[]'),\n",
        "]:\n",
        "    p = pathlib.Path(fp)\n",
        "    if not p.exists():\n",
        "        p.write_text(default)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f'✅ Config OK')\n",
        "print(f'   Gemini  : {GEMINI_API_KEY[:12]}...')\n",
        "print(f'   Pexels  : {PEXELS_API_KEY[:10]}...')\n",
        "print(f'   Model   : {os.environ["GEMINI_MODEL"]}')\n",
        "print(f'   MPT dir : {os.environ["MPT_DIR"]}')\n",
        "print(f'   Agent   : {AGENT_ROOT}')"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": ["## 🔍 Step 2b — Sanity check (run before Step 3)"]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step2b_sanity"},
      "source": [
        "import os, pathlib, requests, json, subprocess, sys\n",
        "\n",
        "ok = True\n",
        "checks = {\n",
        "    'Agent root'   : pathlib.Path('/content/mpt-agent-system').exists(),\n",
        "    'MPT root'     : pathlib.Path('/content/MoneyPrinterTurbo').exists(),\n",
        "    'MPT cli.py'   : pathlib.Path('/content/MoneyPrinterTurbo/cli.py').exists(),\n",
        "    'Queue file'   : pathlib.Path('/content/mpt-agent-system/data/topics_queue.json').exists(),\n",
        "    'Gemini key'   : os.environ.get('GEMINI_API_KEY','').startswith('AIza'),\n",
        "    'Pexels key'   : bool(os.environ.get('PEXELS_API_KEY','')),\n",
        "    'ImageMagick'  : bool(subprocess.run(['which','convert'],capture_output=True).stdout),\n",
        "    'ffmpeg'       : bool(subprocess.run(['which','ffmpeg'],capture_output=True).stdout),\n",
        "}\n",
        "for name, result in checks.items():\n",
        "    icon = '✅' if result else '❌'\n",
        "    print(f'{icon} {name}')\n",
        "    if not result: ok = False\n",
        "\n",
        "# Live Gemini API test\n",
        "print('\n🤖 Testing Gemini API...')\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    key, model = os.environ['GEMINI_API_KEY'], os.environ['GEMINI_MODEL']\n",
        "    r = requests.post(\n",
        "        f'https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/{model}:generateContent?key={key}',\n",
        "        json={'contents':[{'parts':[{'text':'Reply with exactly: GEMINI OK'}]}],\n",
        "              'generationConfig':{'maxOutputTokens':10}}, timeout=15)\n",
        "    r.raise_for_status()\n",
        "    reply = r.json()['candidates'][0]['content']['parts'][0]['text'].strip()\n",
        "    print(f'✅ Gemini responded: {reply}')\n",
        "except Exception as e:\n",
        "    print(f'❌ Gemini FAILED: {e}')\n",
        "    ok = False\n",
        "\n",
        "if ok:\n",
        "    print('\n✅ All checks passed. Safe to proceed to Step 3.')\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print('\n❌ Fix the issues above before continuing.')"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": ["## 📈 Step 3 — TrendScout"]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step3_trends"},
      "source": [
        "import importlib, sys, json, pathlib\n",
        "\n",
        "# Reload to pick up any git pull changes\n",
        "if 'agents.trend_scout' in sys.modules:\n",
        "    importlib.reload(sys.modules['agents.trend_scout'])\n",
        "from agents.trend_scout import run_trend_scout\n",
        "\n",
        "topics = run_trend_scout()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Verify written to correct path\n",
        "qf      = pathlib.Path('/content/mpt-agent-system/data/topics_queue.json')\n",
        "queue   = json.loads(qf.read_text())\n",
        "pending = [t for t in queue if t.get('status') == 'pending']\n",
        "print(f'\n📍 Queue: {qf}')\n",
        "print(f'   Total    : {len(queue)} items')\n",
        "print(f'   Pending  : {len(pending)} ← will be scripted next')\n",
        "print('\nTop 5 topics:')\n",
        "for t in pending[:5]:\n",
        "    print(f\"  [{t['niche']:12s}] {t['title'][:55]}\")"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": ["## ✍️ Step 4 — ScriptWriter (Gemini)"]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step4_scripts"},
      "source": [
        "import importlib, sys, json, pathlib\n",
        "\n",
        "if 'agents.script_writer' in sys.modules:\n",
        "    importlib.reload(sys.modules['agents.script_writer'])\n",
        "if 'agents.llm_client' in sys.modules:\n",
        "    importlib.reload(sys.modules['agents.llm_client'])\n",
        "from agents.script_writer import run_script_writer\n",
        "\n",
        "n = run_script_writer(batch_size=6)\n",
        "\n",
        "queue    = json.loads(pathlib.Path('/content/mpt-agent-system/data/topics_queue.json').read_text())\n",
        "scripted = [t for t in queue if t.get('status') == 'scripted']\n",
        "failed   = [t for t in queue if t.get('status') == 'script_failed']\n",
        "print(f'\n✅ {n} scripts written | {len(scripted)} scripted | {len(failed)} failed')\n",
        "\n",
        "if scripted:\n",
        "    t0 = scripted[0]\n",
        "    print(f"\n--- Sample [{t0['niche']}] ---")\n",
        "    print(f"Title      : {t0['title']}")\n",
        "    print(f"Video terms: {t0.get('video_terms','')}")\n",
        "    print(f"Script:\n{t0['script']}")\n",
        "elif failed:\n",
        "    print('\n❌ Script failed. Check Gemini key in Step 2b.')\n",
        "    print(f"Error: {failed[0].get('error','')[:200]}")"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 🎥 Step 5 — VideoProducer (MPT CLI + Pexels)\n",
        "> Each video takes **3–8 min** on Colab CPU. Start with `batch_size=1` to verify."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step5_video"},
      "source": [
        "import importlib, sys\n",
        "\n",
        "for mod in ['agents.video_producer']:\n",
        "    if mod in sys.modules: importlib.reload(sys.modules[mod])\n",
        "from agents.video_producer import run_video_producer\n",
        "\n",
        "run_video_producer(batch_size=1)  # ← increase to 2 or 3 once first video works"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": ["## 🏷️ Step 6 — SEO Agent (Gemini)"]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step6_seo"},
      "source": [
        "import importlib, sys\n",
        "if 'agents.seo_agent' in sys.modules: importlib.reload(sys.modules['agents.seo_agent'])\n",
        "from agents.seo_agent import run_seo_agent\n",
        "run_seo_agent(batch_size=6)"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 📤 Step 7 — Publisher (optional)\n",
        "> If you skip this step, videos will be queued in `data/manual_upload_queue.json` for manual upload."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_typ  e": "code",
      "metadata": {"id": "step7_publish"},
      "source": [
        "# Optional: run only if you want automatic YouTube upload via OAuth\n",
        "import importlib, sys\n",
        "if 'agents.publisher' in sys.modules: importlib.reload(sys.modules['agents.publisher'])\n",
        "from agents.publisher import run_publisher\n",
        "# Commented out because you preferred manual upload\n",
        "# run_publisher(batch_size=3)\n",
